Name: Bro Falls
About the game: WIN EVERY ROUND TO BE THE LAST FOOD AND GET THE LEGENDARY CROWN! Traps, Falls, Chaos... Brokkoli is angry because nobody chooses him to put in the cart. His evil master plan is that he catches all of the food and drops them into a showdown trial. Foods have to go through traps and obstacles to get out of the trial and beat Brokkoli. BROKKOLI IS ABLE TO ACTIVATE ALL SORTS OF TRAPS IN THE MATCH TO PREVENT FOODS TO COME IN HIS SIDE.
